{
  "stem": "20684.2",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I remember going back to the village before the rest of Poland was liberated because we're a bit higher up, before Warsaw was liberated so it must have been-- when was Warsaw liberated?",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Do you know, by any chance?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It would have been, what, towards the end of '45, 1945, or--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, that was end of '44.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was still-- we already finished-- we were in Poland, don't forget.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it was end of summer, autumn '44, before winter, when I went back to the village-- definitely.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because in '45 I was already in the displaced people's camp in Germany, the end of '45.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was the next year.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we went back to the village and there come the nasty bit.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, this-- the guy wasn't all that good through the war, but things got worse for me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I started running out of luck.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When we got up to the village, we went to visit some of my mother's friends who were still in rags.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she had friends, has it happened three Polish friends, wives of doctors that-- that my father was in charge of the hospital at the time and they were his supposedly good friends and the wives were supposed our good friends.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We found out what they were made of.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And when we got back there, we come to the first one-- and to first friend-- and they didn't want to know us.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She pointed to the back, gave us a little bit of food, says, get away, something about the Jews are all gone, they couldn't believe us.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And a similar thing happened to the second one.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And my mother wasn't convinced yet.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
